the presidential vote originally scheduled for aug 18 was 
moved up three weeks to accelerate the transition of power 
following the june 3 death of ayatollah ruhollah khomeini irans 
revolutionary patriarch 
that transition has been smooth so far despite bitter rivalries 
within the tehran hierarchy between rafsanjanis socalled 
pragmatists and radicals led by interior minister ali akbar 
