including 1000 indian soldiers according to the government 
sinhalese extremists killed 4000 people mostly sinhalese 
government officials and supporters in a backlash against what 
they perceived as excessive concessions to the tamils 
the militant sinhalese have been led by the peoples liberation 
front 
during censorship most references to the front or to sinhalese 
radicals were removed from news stories 
