velvet there ive said it again mr lonely blue on 
blue i love how you love me sealed with a kiss 
everyday of my life and finally in 1974 my melody of love 
his memories of three of his biggest hits 
roses are red came out around graduation time and it 
was a great farewell song 
blue velvet was recorded with 10 minutes left on the 
recording session i didnt pick it and didnt like it 
mr lonely related to lonely people theres loneliness 
in all of us and i felt it i dug back in my soul for this and 
people felt the loneliness 
