vinton was able to maintain a career but many of his peers were 
never as popular again 
they eliminated my competition vinton said about the effect 
the beatles had on male vocalists of his style 
a whole new generation of record buyers is alive now and vinton 
is still competing for their dollars 
i lasted because i made the right songs good honest 
emotional records i do shows and give them a show they cant 
resist so they come back year after year and see me ive changed 
my show to make it fresh make it different 
my music is part of a lot of their lives he said it 
brings back memories their youth their first date their 
marriage so they want to go out and enjoy their early life and 
growing up and all of that 
he feels that hes a much better performer than he was 20 years 
ago 
i was awful then i was young inexperienced nervous and i 
wasnt the confident performer i am today luckily i was able to 
stick around to the point where i can walk on stage today and have 
control of the audience 
being an entertainer is like being a surgeon said vinton 
the longer you do it the better you get at it 
